Package edu.biu.scapi.interactiveMidProtocols.ot.otBatch

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    OTBatchReceiver
    General interface for Batch OT Receiver.
    OTBatchRInput
    Every Batch OT receiver needs inputs during the protocol execution, but every concrete protocol needs different inputs.
    OTBatchROutput
    Every Batch OT receiver outputs a result in the end of the protocol execution, but every concrete protocol output different data.
    OTBatchSender
    General interface for Batch OT Sender.
    OTBatchSInput
    Every Batch OT sender needs inputs during the protocol execution, but every concrete protocol needs different inputs.
    OTBatchSOutput
    This interface is a marker interface for OT sender output, where there is an implementing class for each OT protocol that has an output.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    OTBatchOnByteArrayROutput
    Concrete implementation of batch OT receiver (on byteArray) output.
    OTBatchOnByteArraySInput
    Concrete implementation of batch OT sender (on byteArray) input.
    OTBatchOnGroupElementROutput
    Concrete implementation of batch OT receiver (on group element) output.
    OTBatchOnGroupElementSInput
    Concrete implementation of batch OT sender (on GroupElement) input.
    OTBatchRBasicInput
    Concrete implementation of OT receiver input.
